==Giving Logosia the tomes==
* {{tbox|pic=Tome of the sun detail.png|You show Logosia the tome.}}
* {{tcond|If the player has not handed in all three tomes:}}
** '''Logosia:''' I have not seen this before. Your donation to the library is appreciated.
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{tcond|If the player has one other tome in their inventory:}}
** '''Player:''' You can have this tome which I discovered aswell{{sic}}.
** {{tbox|pic=Tome of the moon detail.png|You hand Logosia the tome.}}
* {{tcond|If the player has the two other tomes in their inventory:}}
** '''Player:''' You can have these tomes which I discovered aswell{{sic}}.
** {{tbox|pic=Tome of the moon detail.png|pic2=Tome of the temple detail.png|You hand Logosia the tomes.}}
** {{tact|below}}
* {{tcond|If the player has not handed in all three tomes:}}
** {{tact|above}}
