** {{tbox|pic=Lamp of knowledge detail.png|You receive an experience lamp as a reward.}}
** '''Logosia:''' If you find any spare pages for these books I would be willing to give you 1,000 gold for each one. Duplicate sources of information are always useful.
** '''Player:''' I'll keep an eye out.
** '''Logosia:''' Enough talk now, Shhhh!{{sic}}
** {{tact|end}}
